
# Golem Warcrafter
Spellcasting	KEY:Golem Warcrafter ~ Spellcasting				SOURCEPAGE:p.n	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Golem Warcrafter Class Feature.SpecialQuality					DESC:At each level, you gain new spells per day and an increase in caster level (and spells known, if applicable) as if you had also gained a level in a spellcasting class to which you belonged before adding the prestige class level. You do not, however, gain any other benefit a character of that class would have gained. If you had more than one spellcasting class before becoming a Golem Warcrafter, you must decide to which class to add each level for the purpose of determining spells per day, caster level, and spells known.
Golem Artisan	KEY:Golem Warcrafter ~ Golem Artisan			SOURCEPAGE:p.n	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Golem Warcrafter Class Feature.SpecialQuality					DESC:The Bonus provided by your Magical artisan feat is increased by 5%% per Golem Warcrafter Level. (Ex 30%% at 1st, 35%% at 2nd, till 50%% at 5th)
Magical Repair	KEY:Golem Warcrafter ~ Magical Repair			SOURCEPAGE:p.n	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Golem Warcrafter Class Feature.SpecialQuality					DESC:At lvl 1, The Golem Warcrafter can now repair golems without mundane materials. The Warcrafter no longer has to pay 50gp per hit point when repairing constructs
Bypass Golem Ward	KEY:Golem Warcrafter ~ Bypass Golem Ward			SOURCEPAGE:p.n	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Golem Warcrafter Class Feature.SpecialQuality					DESC:At lvl 3, By using the Golem Warcrafter's immense knowledge of Constructs you may now ignore a Construct's Magical Immunity. Any Spell you cast now works normally.
Improved Golem	KEY:Golem Warcrafter ~ Improved Golem			SOURCEPAGE:p.n	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Golem Warcrafter Class Feature.SpecialQuality					DESC:At lvl 5, Golem Warcrafter Golems are often better than those constructed by other Wizards or Artificers. This is due to the customization of the golem by the Warcrafter. works as the Improved homunculus feat(Magic of Ebberon) except applies to all constructs created by the Warcrafter

